          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Add Author

This endpoint allows you to add a new author by making an HTTP POST request to the specified URL.

#### Request Body

- `name`: (string) The name of the author to be added.


#### Response

Upon a successful request, the server will respond with the following data:

``` json
{
  "data": {
    "id": "",
    "type": "",
    "attributtes": {
      "name": "",
      "created_at": "",
      "updated_at": ""
    }
  }
}

 ```

The response will include the details of the newly added author, including the unique identifier, type, name, creation timestamp, and last update timestamp.

### Delete Author

This endpoint is used to delete a specific author.

#### Request

- Method: DELETE

- Endpoint: `{{url_v1}}/authors/6`


#### Response

The response for this request follows the JSON schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}

 ```

The response body will contain a message indicating the result of the deletion operation.

### Get Books

This endpoint retrieves a list of books.

**Request Body**  
This request does not require a request body.

**Response Body**  
The response will be a JSON object with a `data` array containing objects representing individual books. Each book object will have the following attributes:

- `id` (string): The unique identifier of the book.

- `type` (string): The type of the book.

- `attributtes` (object): An object containing the attributes of the book including:

    - `name` (string): The name of the book.

    - `author` (array): An array of authors of the book.

    - `description` (string): The description of the book.

    - `publication_year` (string): The year of publication of the book.

    - `created_at` (string): The timestamp of when the book record was created.

    - `updated_at` (string): The timestamp of when the book record was last updated.


The response of this request can be documented as the following JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "data": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "string" },
          "type": { "type": "string" },
          "attributtes": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "name": { "type": "string" },
              "author": { "type": "array" },
              "description": { "type": "string" },
              "publication_year": { "type": "string" },
              "created_at": { "type": "string" },
              "updated_at": { "type": "string" }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

